quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  36,49,"Ma sugayaan (gaaladu) wax kale aan aheyn hal Qaylo{2}, qabaneysa iyagoo murmi.",footnotes:1:[. Erey ahaan macnaha waa dhawaaq ama qeylo daran, waxaana loola jeedaa afuufka koowaad ee Buunka uu dhiman noole kasta oo dhulka jooga digniin hore la’aan.],footnotes:2:[]
  36,50,"Markaas ma karaan dardaaran, ehelkoodiina uma soo noqdaan."
  36,51,"Buunkaa la aafuufi{2}, mise kolkaa bay qubuurahooda ka soo yaaci iygoo u degdegaya xagga Rabbigood.",footnotes:1:[. Waxaa loola jeedaa afuufka labaad ee Buunka, markaasoo ay ka soo bixi doonaan qubuuraha iyagoo la soo nooleeyey.],footnotes:2:[]
  37,34,"Sidaasaan ku fallaa denbiilayaasha."
  37,35,"Waxay ahaayeen marka lagu yidhaah- do: Ma jiro Ilaah (Xaq lagu caabudo) aan ahayn Allaah, kuwa iska weyneeya."
  37,36,"Iyagoo leh: Ma waxaan isaga deynaa ilaahyadayada gabyaa Jinnoole ah?"
  38,13,"Iyo Thamuud iyo qoladii Luud, iyo reer howdkii (loo diray Nabi Shucayb), kuwaa bay ahaayeen xisbiyada."
  38,14,"Ma jiro mid iyaga ka mid ah oo aan beenin Rususha, Markaasay xaq noqotay cadaabi inay ku dhacdo."
  38,15,"Kuwaana (gaaladani) ma sugayaan waxaan aheyn hal Qeylo aanan daah lahayn iyo dib u dhac midna{2}.",footnotes:1:[. Ama fursad. Erey ahaan macnaha xiskin waa waqti u dhexeeya labada lisitaan ee caanaha hasha. Dhawaaqaas waa calaamo Qiyaamaha.],footnotes:2:[]
